title: Time Machine 21 Caravan to China (Choose Your Own Adventure).pdf
description:
IT'S THE YEAR 1272
You have traveled back to the empire of Kublai Khan.

You are in the middle of a desert sandstorm when your caravan is attacked by savage bandits.  Suddenly, a masked figure reaches down and scoops you up onto the back of his camel.

Do you trust this unknown rider or do you break free and jump from the galloping animal?  Your decision can lead you to safety or leave you stranded in time!

ARE YOU READY TO FACE THE DANGER?
Time Machine 21 Caravan to China
by Carol Gaskin
Illustrated by Jose Gonzalez Navaroo

Enjoy!
